(1228, 3, '2016-10-08 00:00:02', '2016-10-08 00:00:02', 'Are you sending us preprinted stock that Arizona Envelope will die cut and convert into envelopes? You must use one of our Layouts when setting up your artwork. Please see the following list of the most popular layouts.\n\n&nbsp;\n<div id="slim-line"></div>\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n	<li><strong><a href="/wp-content/uploads/diecuts/Die_Layout_Instructions.pdf" target="_blank">Die Layout Instructions</a></strong></li>\n	<li><strong><a href="/wp-content/uploads/diecuts/Hobbs_Layout_Instructions.pdf" target="_blank">Hobbs Layout Instructions</a></strong></li>\n	<li><a href="http://azenvelope.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/9-Remittance-6up-on-23x35-Outside-Bleeds.pdf">#9 Remittance 6up on 23x35 Outside Bleeds</a></li>\n	<li><a href="/wp-content/uploads/diecuts/10_1_Up_on_11_x_17_Outside_Bleed.pdf" target="_blank">#10 1 Up on 11 x 17 Outside Bleed</a></li>\n	<li><a href="/wp-content/uploads/diecuts/10_2_Up_on_17_1-2_x_23_OutsideBleed.pdf" target="_blank">#10 2 Up on 17 1-2 x 23 OutsideBleed</a></li>\n	<li><a href="/wp-content/uploads/diecuts/10_4_Up_on_19_x_25_Outside_Bleed.pdf" target="_blank">#10 4 Up on 19 x 25 Outside Bleed</a></li>\n	<li><a href="http://azenvelope.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/10_8_up_on_25_x_38_BLEED.pdf">#10_8_up_on_25_x_38_BLEED</a></li>\n	<li><a href="/wp-content/uploads/diecuts/10_Open_Side_4_Up_on_20_x_28_Outside_Bleeds.pdf" target="_blank">#10 Open Side 4 Up on 20 x 28 Outside Bleeds</a></li>\n	<li><a href="http://azenvelope.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/10-Open-Side-8-up-on-28x40-Outside-Bleeds.pdf">#10 Open Side 8 up on 28x40 Outside Bleeds</a></li>\n	<li><a href="http://azenvelope.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/11-1up-12.5-x-19-Outside-Bleeds.pdf">#11 1 Up on 12.5 x 19 Outside Bleeds</a></li>\n	<li><a href="http://azenvelope.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/6-x-9-Open-End-2-Up-on-19-x-25-Oustide-Bleed.pdf">6 x 9 Open End 2 Up on 19 x 25 Oustide Bleed</a></li>\n	<li><a href="/wp-content/uploads/